# Implementation Plan - NatureSip Premium Application

Rebuild the NatureSip website as a premium, hostable application with enhanced aesthetics, integrated media, and detailed manufacturing documentation.

## Proposed Changes

### Media & Assets
Download and structure all photos and videos from the source site to ensure a self-contained, high-performance application.

#### [NEW] [assets/media/](file:///c:/Users/palla/OneDrive/Desktop/New%20folder/naturesip_media/assets/media/)
- Direct storage for all downloaded images and videos.

### Technical Architecture
Initialize a modern Vite + React project with a focus on "Premium" visual excellence.

#### [NEW] [index.html](file:///c:/Users/palla/OneDrive/Desktop/New%20folder/naturesip_media/index.html)
- SEO-optimized entry point with modern typography links.

#### [NEW] [src/App.jsx](file:///c:/Users/palla/OneDrive/Desktop/New%20folder/naturesip_media/src/App.jsx)
- Root component with Framer Motion transitions and responsive layout.

#### [NEW] [src/index.css](file:///c:/Users/palla/OneDrive/Desktop/New%20folder/naturesip_media/src/index.css)
