### Manufacturing & Process Documentation
Create a detailed "End-to-End Process" artifact for manufacturing/planning.

#### [NEW] [manufacturing_process.md](file:///c:/Users/palla/OneDrive/Desktop/New%20folder/naturesip_media/docs/manufacturing_process.md)
