## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `npm run build` to ensure project integrity.
- Use `browser_subagent` to verify all images/videos load correctly and UI is responsive.

### Manual Verification
- Visual inspection of "Premium" design elements (animations, gradients).
- Verify media playback for all product videos.
- Review manufacturing documentation for completeness and accuracy.
